  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hordes of Cutelings are coming… and they just want cuddles!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot them in the face before they get too close, or risk being overwhelmed by pure, relentless cuteness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294950/extras/aef8d85c6ac1bc945c2f132c6097fd3c.poster.avif?t=1771508633\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294950/extras/aef8d85c6ac1bc945c2f132c6097fd3c.webm?t=1771508633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294950/extras/aef8d85c6ac1bc945c2f132c6097fd3c.mp4?t=1771508633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be the Villain!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive fast-paced 30 to 90-second roguelite rounds on randomly generated maps, each with unique hazards—swamps, booby traps, toxic rivers, freezing cold, and more.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Fighter!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 unique characters, each with their own weapons, stats, and special skills. Every run feels different! Conquer challenges at various difficulties and unlock them all.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Die, Upgrade, Repeat!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death is just another step to power. Upgrade your favorite weapons, invest in your skill tree, and come back stronger to slaughter even more cute things!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294950/extras/6268fa1ae2dd23e1034f70d19bfae457.poster.avif?t=1771508633\" width=123 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294950/extras/6268fa1ae2dd23e1034f70d19bfae457.webm?t=1771508633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
